data.title: Short to U-Hall Razorvine Exec
data.description: Deny Defenders playing U-Hall from aggressively taking a fight with this Razorvine lineup. Defenders may still peek you from U-Hall, however.

data.title: B Site Hookah Arc Rose Exec
data.description: When executing the B Site from Hookah, use this flash lineup to clear the common angles.

data.title: B Long to Spawn Razorvine Exec
data.description: Here's an easy, yet strong Razorvine lineup you can use to disrupt Defenders playing backsite and rotating from spawn.

data.title: Top Truck A Site Arc Rose Exec
data.description: Use this simple, but powerful Arc Rose lineup to flash Defenders holding from backsite.
